        best_for: ['Recent University Graduates fighting intense writer\'s block', 'Professionals seeking visually stunning, modern resume aesthetics', 'Applicants rapid-firing hundreds of applications needing instant Cover Letters', 'People who despise trying to format tables in Microsoft Word'],
        pros: ['The initial "writer\'s block" destruction is unparalleled; it is infinitely easier to edit an AI-generated bullet point than it is to stare at a blank screen trying to remember what you did 3 years ago', 'The sheer beauty of the templates cannot be overstated; a Kickresume PDF looks highly premium and stands out instantly against a pile of boring black-and-white Word documents', 'The ability to change the entire layout structure with one click without the text completely crashing off the page is an incredible technical achievement', 'Generating a highly persuasive Cover Letter directly from the data *inside* the resume ensures logical consistency across both documents'],
