        pricing_overview: `<p>Kickresume operates on a Freemium SaaS model. The Free tier allows users to build a basic resume using a few standard templates and provides limited AI generations. To unlock the massive library of premium graphical templates, unlimited AI rewriting, and the crucial Cover Letter generator, users must upgrade to the Premium tier (billed monthly or annually).</p>`,
        comparison_summary: `<p>Kickresume competes against Resume Worded, Rezi, and Canva. Canva is strictly a design tool with zero logic—ATS software cannot read Canva PDFs. Resume Worded is the ultimate analytics grading engine. Rezi is highly focused on strict ATS compliance. Kickresume differentiates itself by hitting the absolute sweet spot between *Visual Aesthetics and Generative Ease*. If a user wants a resume that looks like it was designed by a professional graphic designer, but wants an AI to actually write all the grueling text for them in 10 minutes, Kickresume is the undisputed champion.</p>`
